File: Eskom has implemented power cuts. Unsplash/Johannes Plenio JOHANNESBURG - Eskom has implemented Stage 2 blackouts from 5pm until 10pm. READ: Gordhan: More sabotage happening at Eskom Power cuts will be repeated at the same time throughout the week due to the continued shortage of generation capacity. The beleaguered utility has been struggling to keep the lights on, implementing Stage 4 power cuts at times last week. Eskom is urging the public to switch off all non-essential items. #PowerAlert2
Due to the continued shortage of generation capacity, Stage 2 loadshedding will be implemented from 17:00 until 22:00 throughout the week. pic.twitter.com/E40GBxaAjs